<subSubSection id="C31E6567FFDAF634811733A5F63BF758" pageId="30" pageNumber="88" type="reference_group">
<paragraph id="8BBB36ECFFDAF634811733A5F755F7BE" blockId="30.[2057,2653,1977,2401]" pageId="30" pageNumber="88">
<emphasis id="B970EAFEFFDAF634811733A5F700F84D" bold="true" box="[2057,2213,1977,2006]" pageId="30" pageNumber="88">Taxonomy.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFDAF63481AF33A5F5F1F84D" authority="Kock, 1978" authorityName="Kock" authorityYear="1978" box="[2225,2644,1977,2006]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Rousettus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="88" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="obliviosus">Rousettus obliviosus Kock, 1978</taxonomicName>
, 
<materialsCitation id="3B6C3CB1FFDAF634811433FCF755F7BE" pageId="30" pageNumber="88">
near Bomboni, 
<quantity id="4CFC9B09FFDAF63481E433FCF6FCF866" box="[2298,2393,2016,2045]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.4" pageId="30" pageNumber="88" unit="m" value="640.0">640 m</quantity>
, Grand 
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFDAF63480C133FCF5F6F866" box="[2527,2643,2016,2045]" name="Comoros" pageId="30" pageNumber="88">Comore</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F313767CFFDAF63481143C18F749F7BE" box="[2058,2284,2052,2085]" name="Comoros" pageId="30" pageNumber="88">Comoro Islands</collectingCountry>
.
</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BBB36ECFFDAF63481143C37F63BF758" blockId="30.[2057,2653,1977,2401]" pageId="30" pageNumber="88">
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFDAF63481143C37F6ABF7D7" authorityName="Kock" authorityYear="1978" box="[2058,2318,2091,2124]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Rousettus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="88" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="obliviosus">Rousettus obliviosus</taxonomicName>
is not a subspecies of 
<taxonomicName id="4C044D6FFFDAF63481153C4BF6ABF7EF" authorityName="G. Grandidier" authorityYear="1929" box="[2059,2318,2135,2164]" class="Mammalia" family="Pteropodidae" genus="Rousettus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="30" pageNumber="88" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="madagascariensis">R. madagascariensis</taxonomicName>
as once thought; genetic studies have shown a clear separation between the two. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
